01:15:27,700 --> 01:15:28,650
Why should we mock at each other?

2707
01:15:28,590 --> 01:15:29,610
[Worried] [Don't laugh...]

2708
01:15:28,700 --> 01:15:29,760
-Don't laugh. -OK.

2709
01:15:29,760 --> 01:15:30,630
[Serious and earnest!]

2710
01:15:30,810 --> 01:15:33,480
[I'm a rapper.(a.k.a. hambugi)]
[Image: Lee Sooji socials]

2711
01:15:31,650 --> 01:15:32,880
No mocking. Right.

2712
01:15:32,940 --> 01:15:33,620
Hambugi.

2713
01:15:33,730 --> 01:15:35,440
Right, bugi bugi ham.

2714
01:15:37,020 --> 01:15:41,220
[The first recording contestant: Taehyun]

2715
01:15:37,160 --> 01:15:38,780
Then I'll record once from the beginning.

2716
01:15:38,780 --> 01:15:40,250
I should be able to record while listening.

2717
01:15:40,250 --> 01:15:41,560
-I'll try once. -Okay.

2718
01:15:41,590 --> 01:15:43,510
[Giving a demonstration as the representative]

2719
01:15:42,000 --> 01:15:42,800
Starting now.

2720
01:15:44,200 --> 01:15:47,490
[Ul! San!  Invincible!]

2721
01:15:47,720 --> 01:15:50,800
[♪ Shout it out loud, Ulsan Whales ♪]

2722
01:15:51,090 --> 01:15:54,290
[♪ Let the world hear us, Ulsan Whales ♪]

2723
01:15:51,180 --> 01:15:54,590
[Former singer]
[Awakening past memories,
recording with passion]

2724
01:15:54,810 --> 01:15:57,810
♪ Shout it out loud, Ulsan Whales ♪

2725
01:15:54,910 --> 01:15:57,860
[Reality is shouting in silence]

2726
01:15:58,140 --> 01:16:01,370
♪ Let the world hear us, Ulsan Whales ♪

2727
01:15:58,370 --> 01:16:01,520
[Representative focus] [Awkward for some reason]

2728
01:16:02,180 --> 01:16:05,030
[Laughing but then having second thoughts—
it's not the time to laugh]

2729
01:16:02,210 --> 01:16:02,980
Ul.

2730
01:16:03,700 --> 01:16:04,620
Ul.

2731
01:16:05,620 --> 01:16:07,240
Ulsan Invincible!

2732
01:16:05,780 --> 01:16:09,500
[OK! That's it.]
[A piece of cake for the first singer]

2733
01:16:07,970 --> 01:16:10,030
-OK! That's it. -Recorded up to here.

2734
01:16:10,120 --> 01:16:12,930
[Cha Taehyun: If it's made like this,
people will understand, right?]

2735
01:16:13,170 --> 01:16:15,570
[Cha Taehyun: Everyone, don't panic.]

2736
01:16:13,270 --> 01:16:15,670
-Everyone, don't panic. -Okay.

2737
01:16:15,790 --> 01:16:18,010
[Show some energy x2. ]
[Everyone can do as they please.]

2738
01:16:18,170 --> 01:16:20,600
[Cha Taehyun: We also added
"Ul! of the Whales"]

2739
01:16:20,910 --> 01:16:22,000
There's also Oh. Oh.

2740
01:16:21,210 --> 01:16:24,250
[Whether it's 'Ul' or 'Oh,'
it's up to you! Ad-libs to enrich the fight song]

2741
01:16:23,700 --> 01:16:24,370
Really?

2742
01:16:24,420 --> 01:16:27,050
[Cha Taehyun: Just add it as a chorus.
Show some energy and improvise.]

2743
01:16:27,330 --> 01:16:30,700
"Ei-hai" is fine too. Just improvise as you like.

2744
01:16:27,890 --> 01:16:30,700
[Oh, ho] [Various improvisations welcome]

2745
01:16:30,710 --> 01:16:31,230
Good, good.

2746
01:16:31,030 --> 01:16:32,750
[Particularly gloomy...]

2747
01:16:31,300 --> 01:16:33,180
It can be added later depending on the situation.

2748
01:16:33,180 --> 01:16:35,060
[So much pressure..]

2749
01:16:33,400 --> 01:16:35,430
-So much pressure. -Listen to the result after recording.

2750
01:16:35,430 --> 01:16:37,580
-If it doesn't fit, we'll just remove it. -OK.

2751
01:16:35,920 --> 01:16:38,210
[Cha Taehyun: If it's fit, just remove it.]

2752
01:16:38,570 --> 01:16:41,250
[Cha Taehyun: Even if you make a mistake,
you can record a second time.]

2753
01:16:41,390 --> 01:16:42,770
[Cha Taehyun: Shout it out confidently!]

2754
01:16:43,010 --> 01:16:44,350
[The rest is repetitive]

2755
01:16:44,190 --> 01:16:46,510
So, feel free to do whatever you want.

2756
01:16:44,660 --> 01:16:46,680
[Feel free to do whatever you want.]

2757
01:16:46,580 --> 01:16:48,520
-OK. -These can all be edited.

2758
01:16:47,220 --> 01:16:49,500
[Director Cha, who inspires confidence]

2759
01:16:48,570 --> 01:16:49,630
Okay, next player.

2760
01:16:49,720 --> 01:16:51,860
I just need to record the "shout it out loud" part, right?

2761
01:16:50,100 --> 01:16:53,060
[The second trainee to take the challenge]

2762
01:16:52,010 --> 01:16:52,910
You'll know it when you hear it.

2763
01:16:52,910 --> 01:16:55,400
-The key point here. -You know the feeling, right?

2764
01:16:53,830 --> 01:16:55,710
Let's just get it over with... it's so embarrassing.

2765
01:16:55,410 --> 01:16:56,850
-I finished first… this is so embarrassing.
- It's all marked here.

2766
01:16:56,270 --> 01:16:58,640
[He's worried too]

2767
01:16:56,920 --> 01:16:58,650
-Sorry…
-Just record while looking here.

2768
01:16:58,650 --> 01:16:59,200
Let's give it a try.

2769
01:16:59,170 --> 01:17:02,550
[Wait! Wait! Wait!] [Hwang Kwanghee, I'll start
with "shouting out loud"too, Director]

2770
01:17:00,740 --> 01:17:02,600
My voice is really loud right now.

2771
01:17:02,820 --> 01:17:03,330
What is it? Please turn it down a bit.

2772
01:17:03,040 --> 01:17:04,630
[Lee Sunbin: Oppa, can he go last?]

2773
01:17:04,180 --> 01:17:04,930
Why? I have to record this myself.

2774
01:17:04,820 --> 01:17:06,990
[After him… I can't do it…]

2775
01:17:07,170 --> 01:17:10,010
I can't believe I got dumped
on this "beggar island"twice.

2776
01:17:07,750 --> 01:17:11,270
[A well-known trainee with an impressive résumé
Image / Footage / Info: MBC]

2777
01:17:10,050 --> 01:17:13,610
This is all your fault—
why did I have to endure four days here?

2778
01:17:12,050 --> 01:17:15,290
[A natural talent that
makes others feel deprived]

2779
01:17:13,610 --> 01:17:15,390
Hiding alcohol…

2780
01:17:15,500 --> 01:17:16,180
-No, no—
-You can't.

2781
01:17:15,530 --> 01:17:16,430
[You can't…]

2782
01:17:16,610 --> 01:17:17,810
[No joking around this time, hyung]

2783
01:17:17,730 --> 01:17:19,080
-Let's try it.
-No joking, seriously.

2784
01:17:18,030 --> 01:17:20,120
[Serious—absolutely no jokes]

2785
01:17:19,220 --> 01:17:20,320
-Do it in one go.
-For real.

2786
01:17:20,320 --> 01:17:22,230
[Director… please don't let me
hear my own voice]

2787
01:17:22,630 --> 01:17:24,110
What now? Here we go again.

2788
01:17:22,790 --> 01:17:24,620
[Extremely sensitive
when it comes to his job]

2789
01:17:25,000 --> 01:17:26,250
[Don't look at me! Don't look at me!]

2790
01:17:25,900 --> 01:17:26,490
Got it.

2791
01:17:26,600 --> 01:17:28,320
-Let's start.
-Everyone out.

2792
01:17:26,710 --> 01:17:28,060
[(Head down) (Head down)
All avoiding eye contact—for Kwanghee]

2793
01:17:28,190 --> 01:17:30,310
[(Looking at the distant hills)
All avoiding eye contact—for Kwanghee]

2794
01:17:28,550 --> 01:17:29,550
Okay, okay, okay.

2795
01:17:30,940 --> 01:17:32,560
[Ah, please…]

2796
01:17:31,550 --> 01:17:33,010
Do it in one go—it's fine.

2797
01:17:33,170 --> 01:17:35,430
[Recording begins in a frozen state]

2798
01:17:35,820 --> 01:17:38,330
[...San! Not! Defeated!]

2799
01:17:38,500 --> 01:17:41,310
San. Not. Defeated.

2800
01:17:38,930 --> 01:17:41,520
[Misses the first beat
right from the start]

2801
01:17:41,620 --> 01:17:44,580
[Ulsan Invincible… Uls… Uls… Uls…!]

2802
01:17:44,700 --> 01:17:45,960
[Uls… Uls… Uls…!]

2803
01:17:46,500 --> 01:17:47,770
[Uls… Uls… Uls…!]

2804
01:17:48,350 --> 01:17:50,030
[Whoa… oh!]

2805
01:17:50,060 --> 01:17:50,600
[Oh!]

2806
01:17:50,780 --> 01:17:51,540
[Oh oh!]

2807
01:17:51,760 --> 01:17:53,370
[Wow~ oh oh!
Like calling out to someone he knows—
an oddly charming shout]

2808
01:17:53,580 --> 01:17:54,560
[Whoa. Oh! Oh!]

2809
01:17:55,220 --> 01:17:58,520
[Facing an overwhelming wall of talent]

2810
01:17:57,150 --> 01:17:58,630
Ulsan Invincible.

2811
01:17:58,700 --> 01:18:01,890
[Like the waves of Jangsaengbo;
♪ Like the waves of Jangsaengpo ♪]

2812
01:18:02,030 --> 01:18:05,420
[Surging~ surging]

2813
01:18:05,560 --> 01:18:08,910
[♪ For the victory of the Whales ♪ ♪ For the victory of the Whales ♪]

2814
01:18:09,020 --> 01:18:12,050
[♪ Let's all shout together ♪]
[♪ Let's all shout together ♪]

2815
01:18:12,310 --> 01:18:15,650
♪ Shout it out loud, Ulsan Whales ♪
♪ Shout it out loud, Ulsan Whales ♪

2816
01:18:15,810 --> 01:18:19,090
♪ Let the world hear us, Ulsan Whales ♪
♪ Let the world hear us, Ulsan Whales ♪

2817
01:18:19,200 --> 01:18:20,540
Like waves,

2818
01:18:20,620 --> 01:18:21,280
[Uls!]

2819
01:18:21,420 --> 01:18:23,280
Like waves, Ulsan.

2820
01:18:22,450 --> 01:18:24,150
[That mournful "Ulsan!"shout!]

2821
01:18:23,280 --> 01:18:27,630
Like rippling water, we will never give up.

2822
01:18:24,300 --> 01:18:27,240
[Tears of overwhelming emotion]

2823
01:18:28,510 --> 01:18:30,910
[Can't hold it back]

2824
01:18:31,580 --> 01:18:34,340
[Shocked]

2825
01:18:38,510 --> 01:18:41,190
[Director Cha thinks this is serious…]

2826
01:18:41,530 --> 01:18:44,840
[Whoa whoa whoa whoa
an artist fighting alone]

2827
01:18:45,970 --> 01:18:51,420
[Artists are just lonely by nature…]

2828
01:18:52,100 --> 01:18:55,020
[(Even his voice is gone QAQ)
Whoa whoa… whoa whoa…]

2829
01:18:55,240 --> 01:18:57,200
[Yoon Namno: He tried so hard,
it just makes it more heartbreaking QAQ]

2830
01:18:57,240 --> 01:18:58,950
[Ul! San! Oh! Oh!]

2831
01:18:59,000 --> 01:19:01,350
Ulsan… whatever.

2832
01:18:59,420 --> 01:19:01,130
[The audience is satisfied]

2833
01:19:01,350 --> 01:19:05,010
Now it feels like we just
watched a sad movie.

2834
01:19:01,690 --> 01:19:03,650
[A perfectly wrapped-up performance]

2835
01:19:04,800 --> 01:19:07,820
[Everyone feels the lingering afterglow]

2836
01:19:05,010 --> 01:19:06,420
The tears won't stop.

2837
01:19:06,420 --> 01:19:07,140
I'm crying.

2838
01:19:07,140 --> 01:19:08,340
Why is everyone like this?

2839
01:19:08,320 --> 01:19:10,720
[Hey, no blaming, remember!]

2840
01:19:10,780 --> 01:19:12,280
[Hwang Kwanghee: Weren't we supposed
to pick the best parts!]

2841
01:19:12,420 --> 01:19:13,770
[Hwang Kwanghee: I added
a lot of color changes]

2842
01:19:14,350 --> 01:19:17,570
[Emotion that won't fade]

2843
01:19:17,430 --> 01:19:18,740
No blaming.

2844
01:19:17,830 --> 01:19:20,750
[Traces of Kwanghee's chaos]

2845
01:19:21,010 --> 01:19:23,780
[No, wait… you guys don't get it]

2846
01:19:24,060 --> 01:19:26,640
If we laugh, we can't use it.

2847
01:19:24,180 --> 01:19:27,210
[At this critical moment,
Director Cha Taehyun remains unfazed]

2848
01:19:26,640 --> 01:19:29,360
So Kwanghee's singing
can't be used as a song anyway.

2849
01:19:27,430 --> 01:19:30,460
[Kwanghee's singing
can't be used as a song anyway]

2850
01:19:29,360 --> 01:19:30,710
It can't be used as a song.

2851
01:19:30,710 --> 01:19:32,910
[Park Boyoung: We recorded so much laughter…]

2852
01:19:32,960 --> 01:19:35,710
Anyway, don't sing like Kwanghee.

2853
01:19:34,590 --> 01:19:36,400
[Don't sing like Kwanghee]

2854
01:19:35,710 --> 01:19:36,520
You know what we need, right?

2855
01:19:36,520 --> 01:19:37,980
What we need is...

2856
01:19:36,930 --> 01:19:39,760
[The director who has
the final say on recording]

2857
01:19:37,980 --> 01:19:39,220
-Shout it out loud...
-The chorus.

2858
01:19:39,220 --> 01:19:40,880
-The chorus and "Ulsan Invincible,"that—
-OK.

2859
01:19:40,110 --> 01:19:42,540
[Decision: Only record the group chorus!]

2860
01:19:40,880 --> 01:19:42,750
I'll just sing the same part as Boyoung.

2861
01:19:42,750 --> 01:19:44,110
[Hwang Kwanghee:
Got it, let's do it again…]

2862
01:19:44,260 --> 01:19:45,720
[Someone please do this properly…]

2863
01:19:45,910 --> 01:19:47,760
[Kwang… not pleased… hyung…]

2864
01:19:46,570 --> 01:19:47,830
-Hyung.
-What?

2865
01:19:47,900 --> 01:19:49,810
[Don't lose heart! Stand up straight!]

2866
01:19:50,220 --> 01:19:51,160
Hurry, stand up straight.

2867
01:19:50,980 --> 01:19:52,770
[Why do I always have
to be the one singing?]

2868
01:19:53,940 --> 01:19:54,610
Kwanghee.

2869
01:19:54,800 --> 01:19:57,280
[I only came because they said I was
delivering a gift—why am I singing…]

2870
01:19:57,120 --> 01:19:58,870
They said I was just delivering
a gift, that's why I came.

2871
01:19:58,870 --> 01:20:00,460
Right? I don't want to anymore.

2872
01:19:58,980 --> 01:20:01,580
[Wasn't this supposed to be a Manito…]

2873
01:20:00,460 --> 01:20:01,780
I don't want to get scolded again.

2874
01:20:01,780 --> 01:20:04,780
[I don't want to get scolded again…]

2875
01:20:05,010 --> 01:20:09,360
[Cha Taehyun, a capital "T"type. Anyway, we can't use this...
If we have to sing later, we'll redo it…]

2876
01:20:09,630 --> 01:20:10,830
I've never done this before.

2877
01:20:09,920 --> 01:20:13,110
[The longest recording session of my life]

2878
01:20:10,830 --> 01:20:13,340
I usually sing for 3 to 5 seconds and it's over.

2879
01:20:13,340 --> 01:20:14,880
[What does that have to do with anything?]

2880
01:20:14,880 --> 01:20:16,430
[Hwang Kwanghee: That's why I'm not a successful singer(?)]

2881
01:20:16,700 --> 01:20:18,750
[Cha Taehyun: You don't need
to sing the whole song.]

2882
01:20:18,960 --> 01:20:21,480
[Why are you still lecturing him!
Stop lecturing him, boss…]

2883
01:20:20,430 --> 01:20:21,760
-I'm not lecturing him.
-Boss.

2884
01:20:21,760 --> 01:20:23,690
[If we're not using it, then fine—
why keep lecturing me…]

2885
01:20:23,460 --> 01:20:25,030
-Why are you doing this?
-I'll go to another company.

2886
01:20:23,790 --> 01:20:24,730
[I'll go to another company;]

2887
01:20:25,030 --> 01:20:26,300
I'll go to THE BLACK LABEL.

2888
01:20:25,120 --> 01:20:27,740
[The artist is having a meltdown]

2889
01:20:26,300 --> 01:20:27,810
He really tried his best.

2890
01:20:27,810 --> 01:20:29,390
If we're not using it, then fine—
why make a big deal out of it?

2891
01:20:27,960 --> 01:20:29,310
[Feeling intimidated…]

2892
01:20:29,390 --> 01:20:33,050
I misunderstood you, Kwanghee. I'm sorry.

2893
01:20:29,630 --> 01:20:32,900
[Quick apology before he runs off]

2894
01:20:33,050 --> 01:20:33,860
OK.

2895
01:20:33,170 --> 01:20:35,020
[Now it's Boyoung's turn]

2896
01:20:33,860 --> 01:20:35,410
Let's begin.

2897
01:20:35,410 --> 01:20:38,670
[♪ Shout it out loud, Ulsan Whales ♪]

2898
01:20:38,900 --> 01:20:42,120
[♪ Let the world hear us, Ulsan Whales ♪]

2899
01:20:42,260 --> 01:20:43,520
Ulsan.

2900
01:20:42,680 --> 01:20:45,570
[As expected of the ace—clears it cleanly]

2901
01:20:43,520 --> 01:20:44,610
OK, OK, that's good.

2902
01:20:44,610 --> 01:20:45,260
Is this enough?

2903
01:20:45,260 --> 01:20:47,080
-That's it, we'll just mix it later.
-OK.

2904
01:20:46,950 --> 01:20:48,870
[So jealous—she sings so well…]

2905
01:20:47,080 --> 01:20:49,210
-OK, OK.
-That was so good.

2906
01:20:49,330 --> 01:20:50,850
[Ah, I can't get any sound out…]

2907
01:20:50,850 --> 01:20:51,920
[Ah! Ah!]

2908
01:20:51,930 --> 01:20:55,100
[♪ Shout it out loud, Ulsan Whales ♪]

2909
01:20:55,260 --> 01:20:58,600
[(Satisfied) A powerful voice
with no worries]

2910
01:20:55,300 --> 01:20:58,800
♪ Let the world hear us, Ulsan Whales ♪

2911
01:20:59,040 --> 01:20:59,770
[Woo—!]

2912
01:21:00,420 --> 01:21:01,220
[Woo—!]

2913
01:21:01,610 --> 01:21:03,550
[Ul! San! In! Vincible!]

2914
01:21:03,680 --> 01:21:05,810
That's a wrap, that's a wrap.

2915
01:21:03,820 --> 01:21:05,740
[Sunbin nails it in one take]

2916
01:21:05,830 --> 01:21:06,790
[Ah, so you can do it like this…]

2917
01:21:07,020 --> 01:21:08,410
[If you don't know,
just shout "Woo!"—that works too(?)]

2918
01:21:08,560 --> 01:21:10,700
[Huh? Really…?
No… there are some (in the lyrics)]

2919
01:21:09,790 --> 01:21:10,990
-Really?
-They're all in there.

2920
01:21:10,990 --> 01:21:12,070
Kwanghee.

2921
01:21:11,120 --> 01:21:14,530
[What on earth have you
been listening to…]

2922
01:21:12,740 --> 01:21:15,280
Oppa, it's not that you can just shout randomly
because you don't know.

2923
01:21:15,280 --> 01:21:17,420
-No, no—
-It's all in the lyrics.

2924
01:21:16,220 --> 01:21:19,880
[Post-performance aftereffects—
mentally dazed]

2925
01:21:17,420 --> 01:21:18,940
I just wanted to get more usable footage.

2926
01:21:18,940 --> 01:21:20,470
I just sing whatever I hear.

2927
01:21:20,470 --> 01:21:23,050
[But isn't there a microphone?]

2928
01:21:21,690 --> 01:21:23,310
-Oppa, it's here.
-It's right here.

2929
01:21:23,240 --> 01:21:24,750
[(Here it is)]

2930
01:21:23,310 --> 01:21:26,590
What is he even saying now?

2931
01:21:24,900 --> 01:21:26,370
[Seriously, all kinds of nonsense…]

2932
01:21:26,590 --> 01:21:29,380
-What microphone are you looking for?
-Honestly…

2933
01:21:26,620 --> 01:21:28,940
[I thought it was that kind of mic…]

2934
01:21:29,380 --> 01:21:31,820
Let's start.

2935
01:21:29,750 --> 01:21:31,490
[Hoon starts recording]

2936
01:21:31,940 --> 01:21:32,810
[Woo—!]

2937
01:21:33,750 --> 01:21:34,650
[Woo—!]

2938
01:21:35,160 --> 01:21:38,520
[Shout it out loud! Ah, wait… (continues)]

2939
01:21:37,180 --> 01:21:38,130
No—

2940
01:21:38,660 --> 01:21:42,020
[♪ Let the world hear us, Ulsan Whales ♪]

2941
01:21:41,940 --> 01:21:45,660
♪ Shout it out loud, Ulsan Whales ♪

2942
01:21:43,030 --> 01:21:45,600
[Though a bit worried about going off-key]

2943
01:21:45,660 --> 01:21:49,740
♪ Let the world hear us, Ulsan Whales ♪

2944
01:21:46,170 --> 01:21:49,320
[Pushes through to the end!]

2945
01:21:50,000 --> 01:21:53,110
[Unexpectedly not easy; Wow, that's high!]

2946
01:21:50,700 --> 01:21:51,660
Yeah.

2947
01:21:53,000 --> 01:21:55,210
OK, OK, nice—just sing it like that.

2948
01:21:53,480 --> 01:21:55,160
[The director is satisfied]

2949
01:21:55,370 --> 01:21:58,040
