2950
01:21:57,750 --> 01:21:58,480
No, you can do it.

2951
01:21:58,350 --> 01:22:01,550
[An anxious trainee vs. a steady director]

2952
01:21:58,480 --> 01:21:59,910
I don't want to sing.
I don't want to sing anymore.

2953
01:21:59,910 --> 01:22:01,380
I'm not giving up.

2954
01:22:01,380 --> 01:22:02,860
-Oppa—
-I'm quitting.

2955
01:22:02,050 --> 01:22:04,370
[I'm quitting…]

2956
01:22:02,860 --> 01:22:05,510
-You can do it.
-I'm quitting.

2957
01:22:05,080 --> 01:22:08,380
