1 trainee prepares alone]

2958
01:22:05,510 --> 01:22:08,350
-I'll take everyone with me.
-You can't quit.

2959
01:22:08,350 --> 01:22:09,420
Anyway, we're quitting tomorrow.

2960
01:22:08,720 --> 01:22:10,550
[Haa… haa…]

2961
01:22:09,420 --> 01:22:10,620
We're quitting tomorrow.

2962
01:22:10,620 --> 01:22:12,000
You can't quit.

2963
