2967
01:22:16,720 --> 01:22:20,020
[♪ Shout it out loud, Ulsan Whales ♪]

2968
01:22:20,060 --> 01:22:23,660
♪ Let the world hear us, Ulsan Whales ♪

2969
01:22:20,220 --> 01:22:23,450
[Clear diction]

2970
01:22:24,140 --> 01:22:26,920
[Flawless, crisp delivery]

2971
01:22:27,280 --> 01:22:28,570
[Hoo-rrr hoo-wah~!]

2972
01:22:28,870 --> 01:22:32,670
[Ooboo-boo-boo-bla!
Singing fine, then suddenly adds extra flair]

2973
01:22:33,730 --> 01:22:34,820
[Hoo-rrr~!
Kind of simple, rustic ad-libs]

2974
01:22:35,380 --> 01:22:36,290
[Boo—kind of simple ad-libs]

2975
01:22:36,650 --> 01:22:37,630
[Goo-goo-goo!]

2976
01:22:40,920 --> 01:22:42,880
[After the chicken,
now come the seagulls]

2977
01:22:45,190 --> 01:22:46,630
[Even Ulsan dolphins join in]

2978
01:22:47,100 --> 01:22:50,050
[Chicken, seagulls, dolphins—
all aboard, setting sail!]

2979
01:22:50,300 --> 01:22:51,600
[Passes out]

2980
01:22:51,830 --> 01:22:54,410
[(Passes out) (Passes out 2) (Passes out 3)
(Passes out 4) 1 person stays calm]

2981
01:22:54,710 --> 01:22:57,990
[She warmed up her voice just for this?]

2982
01:22:56,240 --> 01:22:58,140
She did all that just for this.

2983
01:22:58,850 --> 01:23:00,350
