No—

2987
01:23:04,010 --> 01:23:05,360
[What? You try saying it too!]

2988
01:23:05,590 --> 01:23:08,350
[Cha Taehyun: That's exactly what
the director wants—no, this is great.]

2989
01:23:06,690 --> 01:23:08,550
-Kwanghee, get ready.
-I'm not singing.

2990
01:23:08,550 --> 01:23:09,260
You're last.

2991
01:23:09,000 --> 01:23:10,580
[I'm tone-deaf…]

2992
01:23:10,660 --> 01:23:11,630
OK.

2993
01:23:11,170 --> 01:23:13,560
[Namno starts recording]

2994
01:23:11,630 --> 01:23:14,030
You can come in
a beat late and follow along.

2995
01:23:14,340 --> 01:23:16,450
[Ulsan BBQ pack(?) ]

2996
01:23:16,990 --> 01:23:19,250
[Ulsan BBQ pack(?) ]

2997
01:23:22,970 --> 01:23:24,900
[He said BBQ pack…]

2998
01:23:25,160 --> 01:23:27,540
[Lee Sooji: He said BBQ pack…]

2999
01:23:27,880 --> 01:23:30,310
[(Completely clueless)]

3000
01:23:30,770 --> 01:23:33,070
[ssam… oh!]

3001
01:23:33,550 --> 01:23:35,440
[I think he said ssam (lettuce wrap)…]

3002
01:23:36,100 --> 01:23:37,650
[Kang Hoon: Noona, I think he said ssam…]

3003
