-He was doing fine—
-Wait.

3005
01:23:39,880 --> 01:23:42,130
[Dizzy]

3006
01:23:41,120 --> 01:23:42,670
-Nice.
-Really nice.

3007
01:23:42,550 --> 01:23:44,390
