3008
01:23:42,670 --> 01:23:44,270
-Say "Ulsan Invincible"again.
-Ulsan Invincible.

3009
01:23:44,270 --> 01:23:46,780
Because you said "Ulsan BBQ pack."

3010
01:23:44,810 --> 01:23:46,930
[You said "Ulsan BBQ pack."]

3011
01:23:47,040 --> 01:23:49,780
[He says you said "ssam!"]

3012
01:23:48,480 --> 01:23:50,270
He says you said "ssam"in the middle.

3013
01:23:50,010 --> 01:23:52,420
[As expected of a chef. What a delicious way to sing]

3014
01:23:50,270 --> 01:23:52,540
Really? No kidding?

3015
01:23:52,540 --> 01:23:54,130
No, it sounds like a barbecue set.

3016
01:23:52,770 --> 01:23:54,850
[Witnesses are popping up one after another]

3017
01:23:54,130 --> 01:23:55,250
Barbecue set.

3018
01:23:55,230 --> 01:23:57,220
[Ended up re-recording "Ulsan never loses"]

3019
01:23:55,250 --> 01:23:57,860
Ready, go.

3020
01:23:57,810 --> 01:24:00,830
[Ulsan barbecue set?]

3021
01:24:01,190 --> 01:24:03,160
[Still sounds like that dish]

3022
01:24:01,260 --> 01:24:03,280
Ulsan barbecue set.

3023
01:24:03,300 --> 01:24:04,540
[He said "barbecue set." Haha]

3024
01:24:04,890 --> 01:24:06,980
[Lee Sooji: It's "barbecue set" again.]

3025
01:24:07,200 --> 01:24:10,710
[Ulsan never loses!]

3026
01:24:10,830 --> 01:24:12,050
Okay.

3027
01:24:11,190 --> 01:24:13,340
[After yet another try, finally a flawless "Ulsan never loses"]

3028
01:24:12,050 --> 01:24:13,750
-Okay. Okay. -Nice. Nice.

3029
01:24:13,750 --> 01:24:15,690
-It's "never loses" this time. -Good job.

3030
01:24:14,200 --> 01:24:15,700
[In a hurry to wrap up with a greeting]

3031
01:24:15,900 --> 01:24:17,770
[Okay, last one!] [I'd rather not...]

3032
01:24:17,400 --> 01:24:18,030
Hurry up.

3033
01:24:17,980 --> 01:24:19,870
[I'm going to call the company]

3034
01:24:19,130 --> 01:24:20,850
-Come on, let's go. -I don't want to sing.

3035
01:24:20,850 --> 01:24:23,040
I don't want to sing. I'm just here to send the gift.

3036
01:24:21,990 --> 01:24:23,310
[(Whoosh)]

3037
01:24:23,040 --> 01:24:23,560
Hurry up.

3038
01:24:23,560 --> 01:24:24,320
Give us some few materials.

3039
01:24:24,060 --> 01:24:25,530
[Trying to negotiate] [Hwang Kwanghee: I'll only sing the hook. Just the hook.]

3040
01:24:25,750 --> 01:24:27,960
[The negotiation failed] [Come on, don't be like that. Sing it from the start]

3041
01:24:26,880 --> 01:24:28,250
I only sing the hook. Don't stare at me.

3042
01:24:28,250 --> 01:24:29,630
I won't stare at you.

3043
01:24:30,220 --> 01:24:32,290
[Don't blame me...]

3044
01:24:31,410 --> 01:24:33,070
-Don't blame me... -We won't.

3045
01:24:33,300 --> 01:24:34,930
Okay.

3046
01:24:34,550 --> 01:24:37,740
[Everyone holds their breath, waiting for Kwanghee to try again]

3047
01:24:34,930 --> 01:24:36,400
Ready.

3048
01:24:38,300 --> 01:24:39,310
[Front row fancam]

3049
01:24:40,800 --> 01:24:41,990
Go.

3050
01:24:41,600 --> 01:24:44,490
[Nervous]

3051
01:24:44,790 --> 01:24:48,240
[Trying to match the beat]

3052
01:24:57,000 --> 01:24:59,880
[Sad thoughts... sad thoughts...]

3053
01:25:00,240 --> 01:25:03,040
[A vocalist who lives up to expectations]

3054
01:25:03,460 --> 01:25:06,640
[♪ Shout it out loud, Ulsan Whales ♪] [♪ Shout it out loud, Ulsan Whales ♪]

3055
01:25:06,760 --> 01:25:10,250
[♪ Get lost and wide, Ulsan Whales ♪] [♪ Let the world hear us, Ulsan Whales ♪]

3056
01:25:10,350 --> 01:25:13,810
♪ Get lost and wide, Ulsan Whales ♪

3057
01:25:13,810 --> 01:25:17,230
♪ Like waves, like ripples ♪

3058
01:25:13,890 --> 01:25:16,840
[Words rarely heard in a fight song]

3059
01:25:17,330 --> 01:25:20,820
[We will never give up...] [Ah, never stop... We will never stop]

3060
01:25:20,650 --> 01:25:24,460
We will never give up. Never stop.

3061
01:25:21,110 --> 01:25:23,480
[Total wipeout]

3062
01:25:24,460 --> 01:25:26,180
Shout it out... Whatever.

3063
