[Get lost far and wide. What's that?]

3064
01:25:28,540 --> 01:25:31,380
-Get lost. -Get lost far and wide. What's that?

3065
01:25:29,040 --> 01:25:31,240
[No idea what's going on]

3066
01:25:31,380 --> 01:25:32,520
-You said get lost. -Me?

3067
01:25:32,520 --> 01:25:33,920
Yeah, you.

3068
01:25:33,950 --> 01:25:37,030
[Startled] [Me?]
[You said get lost, Ulsan Whales]

3069
01:25:37,370 --> 01:25:40,350
[Choking up]

3070
01:25:38,190 --> 01:25:39,310
Me?

3071
01:25:39,310 --> 01:25:40,530
It's good. Except you just said "Get lost."

3072
01:25:40,530 --> 01:25:43,070
[Very satisfying at this moment]
[Cha Taehyun: He nailed the "Shout it out" part with the operatic voice.]

3073
01:25:42,660 --> 01:25:43,310
Which part?

3074
01:25:43,180 --> 01:25:45,770
[Shout out loud]

3075
01:25:45,400 --> 01:25:45,960
That part is very good.

3076
01:25:45,960 --> 01:25:47,780
You said you won't blame me.

3077
01:25:46,720 --> 01:25:48,680
[Hard to tell if it's praise or blame]

3078
01:25:47,780 --> 01:25:48,730
I'm not blaming you.

3079
01:25:48,730 --> 01:25:49,660
Hyung.

3080
01:25:49,690 --> 01:25:51,460
[Is this spit? Why is it wet?]

3081
01:25:51,770 --> 01:25:55,160
Get lost far and wide, Ulsan Whales.

3082
01:25:51,770 --> 01:25:55,080
[Holding the receiver tight with sweaty, nervous hands]

3083
01:25:55,290 --> 01:25:56,720
[Hwang Kwanghee: Let's just applaud and get it over with...]

3084
01:25:56,340 --> 01:25:56,990
Wipe it.

3085
01:25:56,990 --> 01:25:57,910
Let's just applaud and get it over with.

3086
01:25:57,800 --> 01:25:58,600
[Let's get it over with...]

3087
01:25:58,830 --> 01:26:01,290
[Tired] [Why did the recording take so long? I thought we're here to send gift...]

3088
01:26:00,650 --> 01:26:01,720
Let's just applaud and get it over with.

3089
01:26:01,720 --> 01:26:04,250
One, two, three.

3090
01:26:04,170 --> 01:26:05,120
[Get lost]

3091
01:26:05,580 --> 01:26:06,250
Get lost.

3092
01:26:06,430 --> 01:26:07,280
[Get lost]

3093
01:26:07,580 --> 01:26:09,550
Get lost. Get lost.

3094
01:26:09,830 --> 01:26:10,630
[Get lost...]

3095
01:26:10,910 --> 01:26:12,150
[Get lost]

3096
01:26:12,250 --> 01:26:15,110
-Get lost. Get lost. -Okay. Okay.

3097
01:26:12,430 --> 01:26:14,370
[Get lost (director included)]

3098
01:26:15,110 --> 01:26:17,140
-Get lost. -Go.

3099
01:26:15,310 --> 01:26:17,010
[Cha Taehyun: Go.]

3100
01:26:17,290 --> 01:26:19,040
[Actors and chefs alike. All of you, get lost]

3101
01:26:19,210 --> 01:26:20,460
[The chef is way too happy]

3102
01:26:19,270 --> 01:26:20,650
Get lost. Get lost.

3103
01:26:20,700 --> 01:26:22,730
[All the directors, just go... get lost...]

3104
01:26:22,740 --> 01:26:24,440
Go. Get lost.

3105
01:26:23,150 --> 01:26:23,710
[Get lost]

3106
01:26:25,030 --> 01:26:27,680
Get lost. One, two, three.

3107
01:26:25,350 --> 01:26:27,650
[Slapping the clapperboard like slapping a mosquito]

3108
01:26:27,680 --> 01:26:28,970
Just go.

3109
01:26:28,010 --> 01:26:30,380
[Filming the moment of glory]

3110
01:26:29,810 --> 01:26:30,700
Don't do this.

3111
01:26:30,630 --> 01:26:32,390
[Stop filming...]

3112
01:26:32,450 --> 01:26:35,850
Get lost. Get lost. Get lost.

3113
01:26:33,310 --> 01:26:35,520
[(Ring finger) starts acting up again out of nowhere]

3114
01:26:35,830 --> 01:26:36,340
[(Get lost)]

3115
01:26:36,480 --> 01:26:37,820
Now, go.

3116
01:26:37,820 --> 01:26:39,660
Get lost, please. All of you.

3117
01:26:38,820 --> 01:26:42,600
[The night Kwanghee wants to be alone...]

3118
01:26:39,660 --> 01:26:41,160
I'm going crazy. Get lost.

3119
01:26:43,360 --> 01:26:44,030
Ulsan.

3120
01:26:43,460 --> 01:26:45,830
[D-2 Trip to Ulsan]

3121
01:26:44,030 --> 01:26:45,900
A 3-day, 2-night seminar.

3122
01:26:45,900 --> 01:26:48,180
We'll disguise ourselves as the camera crew.

3123
01:26:45,950 --> 01:26:50,050
[D-1 Interview]

3124
01:26:48,180 --> 01:26:50,120
Boyoung is wearing the costume.

3125
01:26:50,240 --> 01:26:51,840
[D-DAY This is the last day of Secret Manito...]

3126
01:26:51,850 --> 01:26:54,030
-One, two, three. -Now practice is the only way to survive.

3127
01:26:52,050 --> 01:26:55,470
[Practice is the only way to survive!]

3128
01:26:54,030 --> 01:26:56,350
We have to nail the synchronized dance today.

3129
01:26:56,350 --> 01:26:58,410
If anyone messes up, we're done.

3130
01:26:56,780 --> 01:27:00,530
[Secret Manito D-Day]

3131
01:27:00,620 --> 01:27:02,010
[Whale]

3132
01:27:02,270 --> 01:27:03,540
This is a real rehearsal, right?

3133
01:27:02,340 --> 01:27:05,500
[The last rehearsal before the surprise event!]

3134
01:27:03,540 --> 01:27:05,550
Come out when you hear the signal.

3135
01:27:05,510 --> 01:27:06,420
[The wind is so strong]

3136
01:27:06,550 --> 01:27:07,530
[Are you going to get blown away?]

3137
01:27:07,560 --> 01:27:08,560
[Is it safe in this wind? (Nervous)]

3138
01:27:08,570 --> 01:27:09,770
[The wind is really strong]
[Because of the strong wind, the promotional balloons won't go up!]

3139
01:27:09,770 --> 01:27:13,430
[Because of the strong wind, the promotional balloons won't go up!]

3140
01:27:13,430 --> 01:27:14,850
[Looks like the wind is too strong]
[Because of the strong wind, the promotional balloons won't go up!]

3141
01:27:14,930 --> 01:27:16,600
[Looks like the path Namno took is all uphill...] [One twist after another]

3142
01:27:16,730 --> 01:27:18,330
[This is like climbing a mountain!] [One twist after another]

3143
01:27:18,380 --> 01:27:19,660
[It's too rushed] [Now there's a difference of opinion?]

3144
01:27:19,820 --> 01:27:21,170
[We need a bit more time, don't we?] [Now there's a difference of opinion?]

3145
01:27:21,330 --> 01:27:23,480
[Now there's a difference of opinion?]

3146
01:27:22,350 --> 01:27:23,590
One left.

3147
01:27:23,490 --> 01:27:25,750
