3148
01:27:24,660 --> 01:27:25,830
What should I do?

3149
01:27:25,830 --> 01:27:27,250
We have to hurry.

3150
01:27:26,070 --> 01:27:29,720
[Keep identity hidden]

3151
01:27:29,830 --> 01:27:30,610
We have to do it like this.

3152
01:27:29,840 --> 01:27:31,880
[We must send them our support!]

3153
01:27:30,610 --> 01:27:31,880
Hide here.

3154
01:27:32,010 --> 01:27:33,380
[Talk to me! Talk to me!] [Chaotic rehearsal]

3155
01:27:32,740 --> 01:27:33,460
Taehyun, talk to me.

3156
01:27:33,380 --> 01:27:37,580
[Chaotic rehearsal]

3157
01:27:33,460 --> 01:27:34,960
If we don't double-check, then the result will be...

3158
01:27:34,960 --> 01:27:37,650
We almost missed someone's feelings.

3159
01:27:37,650 --> 01:27:39,910
I guess this is all I can do.

3160
01:27:41,520 --> 01:27:42,760
[Leave it to the fate]

3161
01:27:42,800 --> 01:27:44,460
Manito. Manito. Go for it.

3162
01:27:42,920 --> 01:27:46,190
[Okay, let's start.] [The final battle is approaching]

3163
01:27:44,460 --> 01:27:46,410
Okay, let's start.

3164
01:27:46,390 --> 01:27:47,500
[Okay, confirmed] [The final battle is approaching]

3165
01:27:46,410 --> 01:27:47,590
Okay, confirmed.

3166
01:27:47,620 --> 01:27:48,650
[We're here] [The final battle is approaching]

3167
01:27:48,730 --> 01:27:49,330
[It begins.]

3168
01:27:49,490 --> 01:27:50,250
[Okay, let's start!]

3169
01:27:50,370 --> 01:27:52,250
[Here we go!]

3170
01:27:58,840 --> 01:28:00,140
Wait.

3171
01:28:00,070 --> 01:28:03,230
[Hello, everyone from Ulsan Whale Team!] Hello.

3172
01:28:03,260 --> 01:28:06,300
Hello, everyone.

3173
01:28:06,300 --> 01:28:09,290
We're your Manitos. Come on.

3174
01:28:06,480 --> 01:28:09,630
[We are your Manitos.]

3175
01:28:09,880 --> 01:28:13,770
[We're cheering for you.]

3176
01:28:11,580 --> 01:28:13,860
We made a fight song for you.

3177
01:28:13,860 --> 01:28:15,970
Now I'll show you

3178
01:28:13,960 --> 01:28:18,640
[Always prepared]

3179
01:28:15,970 --> 01:28:16,670
What?

3180
01:28:16,670 --> 01:28:18,370
Unbelievable.

3181
01:28:18,370 --> 01:28:19,250
Amazing.

3182
01:28:19,250 --> 01:28:20,520
Is this a prank camera?

3183
01:28:20,980 --> 01:28:22,910
Let's go.

3184
01:28:21,220 --> 01:28:24,250
[Support from Manito Club] Let's go to the last journey.

3185
01:28:22,910 --> 01:28:24,570
Good luck.
